	* Correct monitor port naming in JackAudioDriver and JackCoreAudioDriver.
	* Big endian bug fix in memops.c (http://bugs.debian.org/cgi-bin/bugreport.cgi?msg=5;filename=11_be24bit.patch;att=1;bug=486308)

